    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver. While mechanically sound and reliable for your everyday needs, it does show its age aesthetically. The exterior has several visible scratches and some minor paint fading on the roof and hood. Inside, the upholstery shows signs of regular use, though it remains clean and functional. It is a solid choice for someone prioritizing utility and reliability over a perfect appearance.",
